node.text:
We get by with a little help from our friends...
Join us and @yondercider this Wednesday (8/11) at 430p as we taste and talk about Friends No. 1, our latest cider collab! Notes of fresh red apple, baking spices, and chamomile abound in this traditionally fermented hard cider—a real delight for the cider heads out there. Friends No. 1 is a limited, draft only release, so grab a buddy and stop by the taproom while it lasts!

#cincymade #cidergeist #yonder #friends4ever

node.text:
Hop in, we're taking a trip up the coastline of imagination.

Our newest Pale Ale, Vision, was the result of a friendly contest for the last slice of pizza in Hood River, OR (more on that later). Brewed to showcase the exciting strobiles we encountered on our last hop selection trip in the Pacific Northwest, Vision is an intensely aromatic, bright, and crisp expression of Mosaic, Comet and Strata. Enough hop character to inspire, with a clean finish that leaves plenty of room for daydreams.

Vision is available exclusively in our new variety pack, the Hop Box, and in the taproom starting 8/13. 

#cincymade #hopbox #vision #hopherald

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Rhinegeist Brewery in Rhinegeist. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
Hops, boxed.
We're stoked to introduce you to the Hop Box! This hopped up variety pack contains four of Rhinegeist's most cherished hop creations, including Vision Pale Ale, a Hop Box exclusive release. Whether you’re heading out with friends, going off the grid for the weekend, or just need some more variety in your life, this mix has the bases covered. What you’ll get:

3 x Truth IPA
3 x Mathlete Low Cal IPA
3 x Knowledge Imperial IPA
3 x Vision Pale Ale (HOP BOX EXCLUSIVE)

The Hop Box will be available in the taproom on Friday, 8/13, and in stores the following week.

#cincymade #hopbox #hopallstars #vision

Congrats to team Truth Hurts, who took home third place from this year‘s @dangerwheel race this past Saturday! Cheers to everyone who participated—we’re looking forward to seeing everybody again next year.

Thursday, August 12th is our first ever movie night in the taproom! We will be screening the classic 1963 Stanley Donen romcom Charade, starring Audrey Hepburn and Cary Grant. Show starts at 8pm. There will be classic theater snacks, themed food and drink specials, and a ‘lawn’ to sprawl out on and enjoy the flic. And the best part: no lengthy previews! 

#cincymade #movienight #charade #letsallgotothelobby

node.text:
It's Franz Friday!
A nod to Cincy’s brewing heritage with a bit of Rhinegeist flair, Franz is our seasonal Oktoberfest bräu. As much at home in a pair of lederhosen as jeans and a t-shirt, Franz is a refreshing climb up the mountain of tradition with a full bodied malt bill and a brisk, clean finish that will pump up your spirits. Franz is a seasonal release, available in the taproom today and in stores starting next week. 

#cincymade #getpumped #maltymountaineer

Glow, our vibrant and refreshing Fruited Sour Ale is an illuminating blend of açaí, prickly pear and passionfruit highlighted with a hint of sea salt. When you're doing your thing, Glow is there to throw a little extra shine. Show us how you Glow!

To find Glow near you, head over to the Beer Finder (link in bio). 

#cincymade #glowup #goskate #rollerskating
